     H            Y.
     F** ABAR02A ***********************************************
     F*  ADJUST FORECAST DATA (ABAEP20) - CHANGE QTY=0 TO 0.1  *
     F*  JW     2024.12.13                                     *
     F**********************************************************
     FABAEP20 UF  E                    DISK
      **********************************************************
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ ABAEP20                  98
     C   98                LEAVE
      * CHANGE QTY=0
     C                     MOVE 'N'       UPDFLG  1
     C           AEORID    IFEQ 'D'
     C           AEEQTY    ANDEQ0
     C                     Z-ADD0.1       AEEQTY
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       UPDFLG
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           AEORID    IFEQ 'C'
     C           AEEQTY    ANDNE0
     C                     Z-ADD0         AEEQTY
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       UPDFLG
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           UPDFLG    IFEQ 'Y'
     C                     UPDATABAEP201
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
